#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Gametype:"
msgstr "Vrsta igre:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Board"
msgstr "Deska"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of possible players:"
msgstr "Število možnih igralcev:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "Four"
msgstr "Štiri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ksquares; is a fun and exciting game. &ksquares; is modeled after the well "
"known pen and paper based game of Dots and Boxes."
msgstr ""
"&ksquares; je zabavna in razburljiva igra. &ksquares; je oblikovana po dobro "
"znani igri Dots and Boxes, ki temelji na pisalu in papirju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The idea behind &ksquares; is to construct squares by interconnecting the "
"dots on the grid. Up to four players can play this game together, taking "
"turns. The trick is – regardless of who has constructed most of the square, "
"it is the player who completes the square that gets the point for it."
msgstr ""
"Ideja za &ksquares; je sestavljanje kvadratov s povezovanjem pik na mreži. "
"To igro lahko igrajo do štirje igralci, ki se izmenjujejo. Trik je v tem, da "
"ne glede na to, kdo je zgradil večino polja, igralec, ki dokonča polje, dobi "
"točko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To win the game round player has to collect the most points by covering the "
"most area with the squares of player's own color."
msgstr ""
"Za zmago v krogu igre mora igralec zbrati največ točk tako, da pokrije "
"največje območje s kvadratki igralčeve barve."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Cilj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "Complete more squares than any of your opponents."
msgstr "Izpolnite več polj kot katerikoli vaš nasprotnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the start of the game, the game board is empty. There is simply a grid of "
"dots showing where lines can be drawn."
msgstr ""
"Na začetku igre je igralna plošča prazna. Obstaja preprosto mreža pik, ki "
"prikazuje, kje je mogoče narisati črte."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "&ksquares; Game Board"
msgstr "&ksquares; Igralna plošča"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each player takes it in turns to draw a line between two adjacent dots on "
"the board. By hovering the mouse over the game board, a yellow indicator "
"line will show you where your line will be placed when you click. Once you "
"have decided where you want to draw your line, click - and the line will be "
"drawn. If by drawing a line, you completed a square then this square now "
"belongs to you and earns you a point. Each time you complete a square, you "
"must draw another line. If your line did not complete a square then the next "
"player(s) take their turn. The game will continue until every square on the "
"board is owned by one of the players."
msgstr ""
"Vsak igralec po vrsti nariše črto med dvema sosednjima točkama na plošči. Če "
"z miško premaknete nad igralno ploščo, vam bo rumena indikatorska črta "
"pokazala, kje bo postavljena vaša linija, ko kliknete. Ko se odločite, kje "
"želite narisati črto, kliknite - in črta bo narisana. Če ste z risanjem črte "
"dokončali kvadrat, potem ta kvadrat zdaj pripada vam in vam prinese točko. "
"Vsakič, ko dokončate kvadrat, morate narisati novo črto. Če vaša črta ni "
"dokončala polja, pridejo na vrsto naslednji igralci. Igra se bo nadaljevala, "
"dokler ni vsako polje na plošči v lasti enega od igralcev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To start a new game with custom settings (number of players, player names, "
"board size) click on the <guibutton>New</guibutton> toolbar button or go to "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item. To start a new game with the same settings as the "
"current game, click on <guibutton>Restart Game</guibutton> button on the "
"toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Če želite začeti novo igro z nastavitvami po meri (število igralcev, imena "
"igralcev, velikost plošče), kliknite gumb <guibutton>Nova</guibutton> orodne "
"vrstice ali pojdite na element menija <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nova</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Če želite začeti novo "
"igro z enakimi nastavitvami kot trenutna igra, kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Znova zaženi igro</guibutton> v orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Pravila igre, strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules"
msgstr "Pravila igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is very little to be said when it come to the rules, as the game "
"concept in itself is rather a simple one. Nevertheless, here are the game "
"regulations you, as a player will defiantly face while playing &ksquares;:"
msgstr ""
"O pravilih je zelo malo za povedati, saj je koncept igre sam po sebi precej "
"preprost. Kljub temu so tukaj pravila igre, s katerimi se boste kot igralec "
"kljubovalno soočili med igranjem &ksquares;:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may only connect the dots on the grid if they are not previously "
"connected by you, your opponent, or the computer."
msgstr ""
"Pike na mreži lahko povežete le, če jih predhodno niste povezali vi, vaš "
"nasprotnik ali računalnik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "To gain the points you have to connect the dots to form a square."
msgstr "Če želite pridobiti točke, morate povezati pike v kvadrat."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The square can be no larger than the four adjacent dots on the grid allow "
"for."
msgstr "Kvadrat ne sme biti večji od dovoljenih štirih sosednjih pik na mreži."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once a square is complete the player who draws the last line of that square "
"is granted the right of possession over it. The square then is colored and "
"the player is given a point."
msgstr ""
"Ko je polje dokončano, igralec, ki nariše zadnjo črto tega polja, dobi "
"pravico do posesti nad njim. Kvadrat je nato obarvan in igralec dobi točko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The player who completes the square is given an extra turn which the player "
"cannot forfeit."
msgstr ""
"Igralec, ki dokonča polje, dobi dodatno potezo, ki jo igralec ne more "
"izgubiti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Try not to play at random. Such game practice will most certainly result in "
"loss."
msgstr ""
"Poskusite ne igrati naključno. Takšna igralna praksa bo gotovo povzročila "
"izgubo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Construct long chains of lines over the gameboard. Once one such chain is "
"complete start to build another one going parallel to the first."
msgstr ""
"Zgradite dolge verige črt nad igralno ploščo. Ko je ena takšna veriga "
"končana, začnite graditi drugo, ki bo vzporedna s prvo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Try not to build contraptions where only one line remains undone. Your "
"opponent will almost certainly take an advantage of it."
msgstr ""
"Poskusite, da ne graditi čudnih izumov, kjer ostane samo ena črta "
"nepovezana. Vaš nasprotnik bo to skoraj zagotovo izkoristil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are to let the opponent get a square or more, try to select the "
"combination resulting in the least damage."
msgstr ""
"Če dovolite nasprotniku, da dobi polje ali več, poskusite izbrati "
"kombinacijo, ki povzroči najmanj škode."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Try to push your opponent into the situation where he/she(it) will have no "
"choice but to let you get the square."
msgstr ""
"Poskusite svojega nasprotnika spraviti v situacijo, ko ne bo imel druge "
"izbire, kot da vam dovoli, da dobite polje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are to get a chance to start completing a whole chain of squares, "
"remember that by leaving two squares at the end of such chain incomplete you "
"are pushing your opponent into completing them, thus giving you the "
"opportunity to continue onto yet another chain. Such a situation is called "
"the double-cross."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dobiti priložnost, da začnete izpolnjevati celotno verigo polj, ne "
"pozabite, da s tem, ko pustite dve polji na koncu takšne verige nedokončani, "
"prisilite svojega nasprotnika, da ju izpolni, kar vam daje možnost, da "
"nadaljujete na drugo verigo. Takšna situacija se imenuje dvojni križ."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
