msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži najboljše rezultate..."
"</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Displays</action> the high score table."
msgstr "<action>Prikaže</action> tabelo najboljših rezultatov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapusti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Quits</action> &ksquares;."
msgstr "<action>Zapusti</action> &ksquares;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &ksquares;…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &ksquares;...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Opens a dialog to configure &ksquares;.</action> See <link linkend="
"\"configuration\">Game Configuration</link> section for details."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odpre pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo &ksquares;.</action> Za "
"podrobnosti glejte razdelek <link linkend=\"configuration\">Konfiguracija "
"igre</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &ksquares; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and "
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections "
"about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega &ksquares; ima skupno &kde; Elemente menija <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> in <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij preberite razdelke o "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">meniju z "
"nastavitvami</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help"
"\">meni Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Pogosto zastavljena vprašanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Želim spremeniti videz te igre. Ali lahko?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Currently the only thing you can change about the game look is the color of "
"the lines. To do so use the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure &ksquares;…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. See "
"<link linkend=\"configuration\">Game Configuration</link> section for "
"details."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno je edina stvar, ki jo lahko spremenite glede videza igre, barva "
"črt. To naredite z menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &ksquares;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. "
"Za podrobnosti glejte razdelek <link linkend=\"configuration\">Konfiguracija "
"igre</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "I have made a mistake. Can I undo?"
msgstr "Naredil sem napako. Ali lahko razveljavim?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &ksquares; doesn't currently have an <quote>Undo</quote> feature."
msgstr "Ne. &ksquares; trenutno nima funkcije <quote>Razveljavi</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play the game?"
msgstr "Ali lahko uporabljam tipkovnico za igranje igre?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &ksquares; cannot be played using keyboard."
msgstr "Ne. &ksquares; ni mogoče igrati s tipkovnico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "I cannot figure out what to do here! Are there hints?"
msgstr "Ne morem ugotoviti, kaj naj naredim tukaj! Ali obstajajo namigi?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. There is no <quote>Hint</quote> feature implemented yet."
msgstr "Ne. Izvedena še ni nobena funkcija <quote>Namig</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Zdaj moram zapustiti igro, vendar še nisem končal. Ali lahko shranim svoj "
"napredek?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid "&ksquares; does not have a <quote>Save</quote> feature."
msgstr "&ksquares; nima funkcije <quote>Shrani</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija igre"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "New Game Dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za novo igro"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "New game"
msgstr "Nova igra"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>New Game</guilabel> dialog consistes of the following "
"groupboxes:"
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno <guilabel>Nova igra</guilabel> je sestavljeno iz naslednjih "
"skupinskih polj:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Players"
msgstr "Igralci"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can change the number of participating players, as well as "
"determine who will be played by human and who by the artificial "
"intelligence. Use the <guilabel>Number of players:</guilabel> spin-box to "
"specify the number of participants. Then type a name for each participant "
"and use the <guilabel>Human?</guilabel> check box to specify the player type."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko spremenite število sodelujočih igralcev, pa tudi določite, koga "
"bo igral človek in koga umetna inteligenca. Uporabite vrtilno polje "
"<guilabel>Število igralcev:</guilabel>, da določite število udeležencev. "
"Nato vnesite ime za vsakega udeleženca in uporabite potrditveno polje "
"<guilabel>Človek?</guilabel>, da določite vrsto igralca."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Board"
msgstr "Igralna plošča"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can regulate the size of the game board. Use the <guilabel>Width:</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Height:</guilabel> spin-boxes to change the width "
"and height of the game board."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko regulirate velikost igralne plošče. Uporabite vrtilni polji "
"<guilabel>Širina:</guilabel> in <guilabel>Višina:</guilabel>, da spremenite "
"širino in višino igralne plošče."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This part of the configuration dialog regulates the difficulty of the game. "
"If you leave the <guilabel>Quick start</guilabel> check box unchecked - the "
"game will begin with the empty grid. Otherwise the game will start with the "
"game board partially filled."
msgstr ""
"Ta del konfiguracijskega pogovornega okna ureja težavnost igre. Če pustite "
"potrditveno polje <guilabel>Hitri začetek</guilabel> nepotrjeno - se bo igra "
"začela s prazno mrežo. V nasprotnem primeru se bo igra začela z delno "
"zapolnjeno igralno ploščo."

